des:
Mall de las Aguilas’s skill will let you know all the important information and happenings at the center. Whether you’re curious what type of stores they have, where to get a rideshare, when they will be closing, or what the next upcoming event is, download this skill to be informed on all things at Mall de las Aguilas. You can access this skill on any of your Alexa devices.

To get started, enable Liberty Center’s skill through the Alexa App or by saying, “Alexa, open Mall de las Aguilas.”

If you’re having trouble, please visit www.malldelasaguilas.com.
